Package: onet2r
Title: Work with 'O*NET' Web Services, Archives, and Weights
Version: 0.4.1
Authors@R:
    person("Alex", "Farach", email = "alexfarach@microsoft.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: Access the 'O*NET' Web Services Application Programming Interface
    (API) version 2.0. Search occupations, retrieve occupation details such as
    skills, knowledge, abilities, tasks, and work activities, access database
    tables, perform taxonomy crosswalks, join wage and employment context,
    assemble longitudinal archive panels, and validate user-supplied
    occupational measures. Results are returned as tibbles for easy integration
    with tidyverse workflows.
